Story: Read a file and count words

Given:
  filename: String = "test-input.txt"
  content: String = ""
  word_count: Integer = 0

Step 1 → Read file content
  Effect: Read filename into content
  Because: Load text data for processing

Step 2 → Count words in content
  Because: Calculate total word count from text
  Then: word_count becomes length of split content by spaces

Step 3 → Display result
  Effect: Print "Word count: {word_count}"
  Because: Show results to user

End: Return word_count
